Meal 1 ( lunch / brunch)
  * Simple Carrot Leek Soup. 
    - 2 tbsp Ghee
    - 3 med leeks
    - 2 tsp fresh thyme
    - 2 tsp real salt
    - 4 ribs celery
    - 2 lbs carrots
    - 5 cups chx broth
    - 1 cup sour cream
Meal 2 (dinner / supper)
  * Ribeye, Potatoes, and Cabbage. 
    - Ribeye 
    - Waxy Potato
    - Green Cabbage
    - 1 tbsp of Butter


